<section>
	<h2>Purpose</h2>
	<p>This plugin makes an AJAX request when a form is submitted.</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Use when</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>When making AJAX request for submitting a form</li>
	</ul>
</section>

