<section>
	<h2>How to implement</h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Create a <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> element and set <code>method</code> and <code>action</code> attributes
			<pre><code>&lt;form action="#target-link" method="POST"&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>
		</li>
		<li>Within the <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> element, add a submit <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> element with <code>class="provisional wb-onpage-submit"</code> and <code>type="submit"</code>.
			<pre><code>&lt;form action="#target-link" method="POST"&gt;&lt;button class="provisioanl wb-onpage-submit" type="submit"&gt;Submit&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>
		</li>
	</ol>
</section>

